{"id":1919881,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Gakuto Kajiwara (梶原 岳人, Kajiwara Gakuto) is a Japanese voice actor and singer from Osaka Prefecture. He is affiliated with Haikyō. He is best known for voicing Asta in Black Clover, Shinra Kusakabe in Fire Force, and Hitohito Tadano in Komi Can't Communicate, Luka in Honkai: Star Rail, and Hiiro Amagi in Ensemble Stars!.","name":"Gakuto Kajiwara","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"카지와라 가쿠토","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"梶原岳人是日本的男性聲優、歌手、YouTuber。出身於大阪府，所屬經紀公司為東京俳優生活協同組合。所屬唱片公司是 avex pictures。","name":"梶原岳人","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"梶原岳人","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"梶原岳人是一名日本男性声优、歌手、YouTuber。大阪府出身。所属经纪公司为东京俳优生活协同组合。所属唱片公司是avex pictures。","name":"梶原岳人","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Gakuto Kajiwara","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Gakuto Kajiwara es un actor de doblaje y cantante japonés de la prefectura de Osaka. Está afiliado a Haikyō. Es más conocido por prestar su voz a Asta en Black Clover, a Shinra Kusakabe en Enen no Shouboutai, a Hitohito Tadano en Komi-san no puede comunicarse, a Luka en Honkai: Star Rail y a Hiiro Amagi en Ensemble Stars!","name":"Gakuto Kajiwara","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Gakuto Kadžiwara","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"b